      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POWER SQUEEZE (8) broke from the inside draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only 1.3 lengths (41.39) behind Firethorn at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Winning claims. FADE TO BLACK (1) ran below his best last time finishing sixth (35.23) over 600m at this track in a Grade 5. Has a good record at this journey. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Likely to play a prominent role. STARFIRE TEARS (3) has been thereabouts without winning, the latest finishing fourth (41.99) off a wide draw at this track in a OPEN. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. Got the money at her only try from this box. Can do much better this time. STOWAWAY (2) can fill a top-three spot.",
